OL,3,CWoman arrested after alleged racial
OL,4,Cincident outside mosque
OL,6,FA 36-year-old woman has been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing an alleged racial incident
OL,8,Foutside a Jersey mosque yesterday
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,11,FThe woman has been remanded in police
OL,12,Fcustody and is assisting officers with
OL,13,Ftheir enquiries.
OL,15,FPolice were called to the island's
OL,16,FIslamic Centre on Aquila Road, in St
OL,17,FHelier, just after 2pm on Friday 6
OL,18,FMarch.
