OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1773072686
OL,3,CWoman arrested after alleged racial
OL,4,Cincident outside mosque
OL,6,FA 51-year-old male has been charged
OL,7,Fwith disorderly conduct in relation to
OL,8,Fthe same incident, and is due to
OL,9,Fappear at the island's Magistrates
OL,10,FCourt on 1 April.
OL,12,FPolice say the investigation remains
OL,13,Fongoing, and officers are appealing to
OL,14,Fwitnesses to come forward with
OL,15,Finformation.
