OL,6,FThe Force's Community Safety Team say
OL,7,Fthey are supporting members of the
OL,8,FMuslim community, and will be
OL,9,Fconducting patrols around the Mosque
OL,10,Ffor the remainder of Ramadan, which
OL,11,Fends on Thursday 19 March.
